你能够调用以下的API:
[['SocialSecurity.get_pension_contribution_rate', {'name': 'SocialSecurity.get_pension_contribution_rate', 'description': 'Get the pension contribution rate and base for a specific city.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'city', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the city name'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'contribution_rate', 'description': 'the pension contribution rate.'}, {'name': 'contribution_base', 'description': 'the pension contribution base.'}]}], ['SocialSecurity.get_retirement_policy', {'name': 'SocialSecurity.get_retirement_policy', 'description': 'Get the retirement policy for a specific city.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'city', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the city name'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'retirement_age', 'description': 'the retirement age.'}, {'name': 'pension_calculation_method', 'description': 'the method to calculate pension.'}]}], ['FinancialAdvisor.get_retirement_planning_advice', {'name': 'FinancialAdvisor.get_retirement_planning_advice', 'description': 'Get retirement planning advice based on current age, retirement age, current income, and expected retirement income.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'current_age', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the current age of the person.'}, {'name': 'retirement_age', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the expected retirement age.'}, {'name': 'current_income', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the current annual income.'}, {'name': 'expected_retirement_income', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the expected annual retirement income.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'advice', 'description': 'the retirement planning advice.'}]}], ['RetirementCalculator.estimate_retirement_expenses', {'name': 'RetirementCalculator.estimate_retirement_expenses', 'description': 'Estimate the retirement expenses based on current age, retirement age, current income, expected retirement income, and life expectancy.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'current_age', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the current age of the person.'}, {'name': 'retirement_age', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the expected retirement age.'}, {'name': 'current_income', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the current annual income.'}, {'name': 'expected_retirement_income', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the expected annual retirement income.'}, {'name': 'life_expectancy', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the expected life expectancy after retirement.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'estimated_expenses', 'description': 'the estimated retirement expenses.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
